narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This is a great course because KvK is so awesome! The readings and movies were really awesome. She also makes the course very flexible - which allows it to be kind of personalized. If the class needs more time/less time on one concept, she adjusts accordingly.
I struggled throughout the course but felt comfortable with the material

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Great course! A really complicated, tough language but not an overwhelming workload - def the best slavic language choice if you're looking for a fun class where you can do well!
